Class UserAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • owlSpeak.engine.his.UserAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UserActionSemantics, UserActionVariables

    public abstract class UserAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements IUserAction
    The UserAction class encapsulates a user action which consists of a Move object and a Map defining fields with their addressed Semantics.
